data.description:
Welcome to this extraordinary home on a one-acre lot with an impressive long driveway, creating a private and picturesque setting. Less than 3 years old, this residence offers 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, a flex room, an office, and an open-concept design with wood floors, complemented by crown molding in living areas and the owner's suite.

Step outside to your backyard oasis featuring a heated pool with a spa, adorned by a fully mature European fan palm tree. The extra-large covered gazebo adds a perfect touch for relaxation and entertainment. A stone-framed wood-burning fireplace enhances the cozy ambiance of the living space.

Inside, discover ample storage with strategically placed closets throughout. The chef's kitchen is equipped with numerous cabinets for all your culinary needs. This property, in a quiet cul-de-sac with great neighbors, offers a harmonious blend of luxury and practicality. Don't miss the chance to call this house your dream home!
